$interpreted: Experiment: Garrr~ ruuu~ Rune~
Experiment: Gao!
Bandit Goon: Is this the place? Th...that research lab with a lot of valuables?
Bandit Leader: We'll know once we check out what's inside.
Bandit Goon: B-But I heard rumors about constant screams coming from within the lab. Maybe there really are monsters and stuff inside...
Bandit Leader: You idiot! Quit talking nonsense!
Bandit Leader: It already looks pretty darn weird. Perhaps there really is treasure...
Bandit Goon: Boss, there's a crystal statue right ahead!
Bandit Leader: It moves!? What the hell is this monstrosity?
Experiment: Gaooo~
Bandit Leader: Monster! Stay away from me!
Bandit Goon: Boss, got any other plans?
Bandit Leader: I got it. Take this!
Bandit Goon: Huh, turns out it can be easily dealt with. Who knew?
Bandit Leader: Hehe, this big fella fainted from just the shock~
Bandit Leader: Hey, check out what's behind its neck.
Bandit Goon: Woah, that's a big gemstone. Even I can tell how much money that's gonna sell!
Bandit Leader: Taking the entire statue seems quite unrealistic for just the two of us. I say we dig out that gemstone first?
Bandit Goon: B-But how are we going to dig it out?
Bandit Leader: Seriously? Are you that dumb? Just knock it loose with the knife~
Bandit Goon: Knock? W-What if I break it? What should I do then?
Bandit Leader: Hehe~ If you knock it into pieces...we'll grab an arm, maybe a leg. Bet those are pretty valuable too~
Bandit Goon: Ohh~ Boss, you're so smart!
Yamitsuki: What are you doing!?
Yamitsuki: ...Leave, or do you prefer death instead?
Bandit Leader: Damnit, let's go!
Aosta: What's with all the ruckus?
Yamitsuki: ...Bandits.
Aosta: Hmph, looks like I need to put up a defensive barrier. I cannot allow random people to trespa...hmm?
Aosta: This mess...what happened here?
Aosta: MX46!
Yamitsuki: It's alright...
Aosta: Professor's items!
Experiment: Ru~
Aosta: You worthless...
Experiment: Grrr~ Ruuu~
Aosta: You...you are not like him at all!
Yamitsuki: Aosta, calm down!
Aosta: I don't need him anymore.
Aosta: Yamitsuki, remove the gemstone.
Yamitsuki: B-But...
Aosta: Remove, the gemstone!
Yamitsuki: U-Understood.
Aosta: Go after him!
